  1990→// InternalGatewayServiceAnnotation represents the hostname of the service a gateway will use. This is
  1991→// only used internally to transfer information from the Kubernetes Gateway API to the Istio Gateway API
  1992→// which does not have a field to represent this.
  1993→// The format is a comma separated list of hostnames. For example, "ingress.istio-system.svc.cluster.local,ingress.example.com"
  1994→// The Gateway will apply to all ServiceInstances of these services, *in the same namespace as the Gateway*.
  1995→const InternalGatewayServiceAnnotation = "internal.istio.io/gateway-service"
